headline: Global ETF Assets Tracking MSCI Equity Indexes Exceed $2 Trillion
summary: NEW YORK, July 16, 2025--The assets in indexed equity exchange-traded funds (ETFs) linked to MSCI’s global equity indexes surpassed $2 trillion, a growth rate of 17 percent since the start of 2025.
